## Void
Void object in Python
[pypi](https://pypi.org/project/void/)

## Installation
```shell
pip install void
```

## Example usage
```python
from void import Void

In [1]: Void is Void() is Void.method()
Out[1]: True

In [2]: Void['get']['void'] is Void
Out[2]: True

In [3]: list(Void) or [for x in Void]
Out[3]: []

# set{attr,item} is also supported
```
